---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const RELEASE_DATE_LABEL = "September 15, 2026";
---

<Layout
	title="You're in — Sacred Struggle"
	description="Pre-order confirmation for Sacred Struggle by Marcel Samyn."
>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40">
		<header class="mb-12">
			<p class="mb-4 font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-orange-700">
				Pre-order confirmed
			</p>
			<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-blue-800 md:text-5xl">
				You&rsquo;re in.
			</h1>
		</header>

		<section class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
			<p>
				Thank you. Truly.
			</p>
			<p>
				The first version of <em class="font-serif">Sacred Struggle</em>&mdash;in PDF and
				ePub&mdash;will land in your inbox on
				<strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">{RELEASE_DATE_LABEL}</strong>.
				Every future version after that comes to you free, automatically.
			</p>
			<p class="text-base text-gray-500">
				I&rsquo;ll be sending from <span class="font-mono text-gray-700">marcel@samyn.co</span>&mdash;please
				add it to your contacts so it doesn&rsquo;t get lost in spam.
			</p>
			<p class="text-base text-gray-500">
				If anything looks off, just reply to your Stripe receipt or email me directly.
			</p>
		</section>

		<div class="mt-16">
			<a
				href="/"
				class="text-blue-600 underline decoration-blue-300 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-orange-600 hover:decoration-orange-300"
			>
				← Back to kalon.solutions
			</a>
		</div>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>
